-- allium: 3
-- reference-kommo-ui-kit.allium
--
-- REFERENCE SPEC: Distilled from kommo-crm/crm-react-ui-kit (2026-05-09)
-- Purpose: UI-pattern inspiration catalogue for JobSync CRM (Roadmap Sektion 5)
-- Source: /home/pascal/projekte/kommo-crm-ui-kit/
-- NOT an implementation target — used as visual/interaction pattern reference only.
--
-- DISTILLATION RESULT: No domain-level entities, rules, or invariants found.
-- This codebase is a pure UI primitive library (React components + CSS Modules).
-- All content is implementation-level (component props, CSS custom properties,
-- theme tokens). A product owner would not include any of it in requirements.
--
-- Scope: Full library examined
-- Examined: src/components/ (27 components), src/lib/ (theme, keyboard, platform),
--           src/hooks/, src/stylesheets/ (304-line CSS custom property theme)
-- Finding: Zero behavioural domain concepts. Library is stateless UI primitives.
--
-- Includes: Component catalogue and theming model (for reference only)
-- Excludes: Everything — no domain to specify
--
-- COMPONENT CATALOGUE (for UI-pattern inspiration, not Allium entities):
--
--   Form Controls:
--     Button (themes: neutral, primary, secondary, danger-primary, danger-tertiary,
--             icon-secondary, icon-ghost, icon-danger-ghost, icon-small-ghost,
--             icon-small-danger-ghost, context, icon-context)
--     Input (with invalid description placement: bottom | right)
--     BaseInput (shared input foundation)
--     InlineInput (inline editing)
--     TextArea (auto-resize hook)
--     Select (with nested Item, List, Button, Arrow, Icon sub-components)
--     SelectButton (standalone select trigger)
--     Checkbox (checked styles: mark | indeterminate)
--     CheckboxGroup (with Checkbox, CheckboxSelectAll, ItemRoot sub-components)
--     RadioGroup (with Radio, ItemRoot sub-components)
--     Switcher (toggle switch)
--     VisuallyHiddenInput (accessible hidden input)
--
--   Layout:
--     Accordion (single | multiple mode, with Item sub-component)
--     Separator (orientation: horizontal | vertical)
--     List (generic list container)
--     ContentBlock (content grouping)
--     Portal (React portal wrapper)
--
--   Feedback:
--     Badge (themes: neutral, promo, info, safety, warning, danger)
--     CounterBadge (numeric badge)
--     Spinner (loading indicator)
--     Callout (alert/info banner)
--     Label (form label)
--
--   Navigation:
--     FilterTabs (orientation: horizontal | vertical)
--     ContextMenu (wraps Radix DropdownMenu)
--     Link (styled anchor)
--
--   Infrastructure:
--     ConfigProvider (sets appearance theme on document root)
--     Text (typography primitive)
--
-- THEMING MODEL:
--   Appearance enum: default | alternative (dark mode)
--   Applied via: data-crm-ui-kit-theme attribute on document.documentElement
--   Token system: ~184 CSS custom properties (--crm-ui-kit-*)
--   Per-component theme objects override base tokens
--   Styling: CSS Modules (*.module.css per component)
--
-- VALUE FOR JOBSYNC:
--   1. Component taxonomy — what primitives a CRM UI kit considers essential
--   2. Theme token granularity — per-component CSS variable overrides
--   3. Badge semantic categories — neutral/promo/info/safety/warning/danger
--   4. Button variant spectrum — neutral through danger with icon/context variants
--   5. Checkbox indeterminate pattern — useful for bulk-select in CRM lists
--   6. FilterTabs orientation — horizontal for desktop, vertical for mobile
--   7. Radix DropdownMenu wrapping — ContextMenu as compositional wrapper
--
-- Since there are no domain concepts to specify, this file serves as
-- a structured reference catalogue only. No entities, rules, or invariants.
